<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Kan nunnak a herh bik mi, dawtnak le zangfahnak
 Bawipa kan pe hram ko,
 Kan herhmi ngandamnak le, Bawipa na zaangfahnak
 Kan nih kan ruahchan.

[C1]
   Khamhtu, a thawng Pathian kan ngei
   Tlangthial khawh thawnnak neitu, khawnhtu Pathian asi,
   A zungzal, in khamhtu Bawi asi, thlanchung in a thothan i
   Jesuh thihnak a tei.

[V2]
 Ka sining vialte kan pek, ka nunnak vialte dihlak
 Na kut chungah an um,
 Bawipa na duh bantuk in, ka nunnak le ka sining
 Na sinah ka ra.

[B1]
   Na ceunak cu, Lei cung mi sinah
   Thangthat, sunglawi chin seh a nung Siangpahrang,
   Jesuh, Na ceunak cu, lei cung mi sinah
   Thangthat, sunglawi chinseh a nung Siangpahrang.</lyrics>
<title>A THAWNG PATHIAN</title>
</song>